Bug report 1 (SCRUM-80 with attachment)
https://beetroot2024.atlassian.net/browse/SCRUM-80 

Title: On the “Create Your Account” page some of the patient information text fields are not fully displayed in a range of window widths. 

Description: The window widths of 483 to 625 do not display the full patient information text fields on the “Create Your Account” page (https://signup.mayoclinic.org/?applicationId=6fd03569-c4c9-439c-bbcb-931305671b6d).

Steps to reproduce: 
1. Go to the “Create Your Account” page: from home page, click on “Log in” and then on “Create Account”
2. Minimize the web page to a width of between 483 and 625.
3. Notice the patient information text fields are not fully visible.

Actual result: Patient information text fields are not fully visible on window widths between 483 and 625.
Expected result: Patient information text fields are fully visible at any window width at least equal to the widest text field.

Severity: Low
Priority: Low

Environment: Windows 11, Firefox version 123.0 (64-bit).

